{% comment %}
  Yotpo widgets loader. Emits the single per-store loader script that
  hydrates every `.yotpo-widget-instance` on the page (the product-card
  reviews stars). Gated on the reviews flag + a configured store App Key,
  so it's inert until a merchant pastes their key in theme settings.
  Include once per page that shows reviews (currently the brand page).
{% endcomment %}
{% if settings.aico_reviews_enabled and settings.aico_yotpo_app_key and settings.aico_yotpo_app_key != '' %}
  <script async src="https://cdn-widgetsrepository.yotpo.com/v1/loader/{{ settings.aico_yotpo_app_key }}"></script>
{% endif %}
